snippet.title: Renowned Explorers: The Emperor's Challenge - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.gog.com/game/renowned_explorers_the_emperors_challenge

This expansion pack for Renowned Explorers takes you all the way to the Far East. It’s packed with new content and also provides an entirely new way to play the game! The main features are:

Four new characters: Suh Min-Jeong, Hojo Fumiaki, Wang Yu and Phailin Boonyasak. All with their own unique abilities and personalities.
An entirely new expedition called the Anagogic Archipelago, in which you travel across a set of scattered Indonesian islands.
The Emperor’s Challenge: a new game mode in which you’re given many crazy challenges and try to beat Rivaleux to the punch in completing them.
